----------------logrotate---------------



apt-get install logrotate -y
+++
cat << EOF > /etc/logrotate.d/rsyslog
/opt/**/*.log
{ 
weekly
missingok
notifempty 
compress 
minsize 15M
} 
EOF
+++

   проверка
